excerpts.description:
This example</para> <itemizedlist>
 <listitem>
   <para>creates an &SNS; FIFO topic, two &SQS; FIFO queues, and one Standard queue.</para>
  </listitem>
  <listitem>
   <para>subscribes the queues to the topic and publishes a message to the topic.</para>
  </listitem>
</itemizedlist>
 <para>The <ulink
   url="https://github.com/awsdocs/aws-doc-sdk-examples/tree/main/javav2/example_code/sns/src/test/java/com/example/sns/PriceUpdateExampleTest.java"
   >test</ulink> verifies the receipt of the message to each queue. The <ulink
   url="https://github.com/awsdocs/aws-doc-sdk-examples/tree/main/javav2/example_code/sns/src/main/java/com/example/sns/PriceUpdateExample.java"
   >complete example</ulink> also shows the addition of access policies and deletes the resources at
  the end.
